original_title: Ruang Rupa Radio of Rock Tour Serial 2
overview: The story of Efek Rumah Kaca, White Shoes & Couple Company, Goodnight Electric, Sangkakala, and other bands to meet their fans and recognizing the music scene in each cities by taking a tour entitled “Radio of Rock Tour Serial 2” from the city of Purwokerto, Malang, Surabaya to Denpasar.
title: Ruang Rupa Radio of Rock Tour Serial 2
